00:25:52.400 --> 00:25:53.420
Yeah, the

00:25:53.420 --> 00:25:54.060
intellect becomes

00:25:54.060 --> 00:25:54.620
different things.

00:25:54.720 --> 00:25:55.160
I mean, since

00:25:55.160 --> 00:25:56.720
the most profound

00:25:56.720 --> 00:25:58.740
thing our time with

00:25:58.740 --> 00:26:00.060
Deleuze's The

00:26:00.060 --> 00:26:01.200
Logic of Sense did

00:26:01.200 --> 00:26:02.180
for me, it's just

