00:26:29.540 --> 00:26:31.940
difference or a

00:26:31.940 --> 00:26:33.740
deflection in, you

00:26:33.740 --> 00:26:35.180
know, velocity and

00:26:35.180 --> 00:26:35.760
direction.

00:26:36.360 --> 00:26:37.380
You know, when I

00:26:37.380 --> 00:26:38.680
see that this may

00:26:38.680 --> 00:26:40.100
look like an

00:26:40.100 --> 00:26:43.200
opposition or a

00:26:43.200 --> 00:26:44.000
paradox between

00:26:44.000 --> 00:26:45.600
consciousness and

00:26:45.600 --> 00:26:46.980
the body, you

00:26:46.980 --> 00:26:47.340
know, I see, well,

00:26:47.400 --> 00:26:48.360
different articulations,

00:26:48.540 --> 00:26:49.460
different senses of

00:26:49.460 --> 00:26:50.620
intellect, of body and

00:26:50.620 --> 00:26:51.460
their relationship to

00:26:51.460 --> 00:26:51.840
each other.

00:26:52.000 --> 00:26:53.240
Sure, the intellect

00:26:53.240 --> 00:26:54.000
can be that

00:26:54.000 --> 00:26:54.880
