00:26:56.760 --> 00:26:57.320
be remade.

00:26:57.540 --> 00:26:58.220
That's one of the

00:26:58.220 --> 00:26:58.760
things for me, I

00:26:58.760 --> 00:26:59.580
mean, I kind of

00:26:59.580 --> 00:27:00.040
think we've talked

00:27:00.040 --> 00:27:00.580
about this before,

00:27:00.640 --> 00:27:01.740
but I think for me,

00:27:01.820 --> 00:27:03.160
in order to say, and

00:27:03.160 --> 00:27:03.680
you hear this all

00:27:03.680 --> 00:27:04.220
the time, it's like

00:27:04.220 --> 00:27:04.900
Nietzsche will

00:27:04.900 --> 00:27:05.760
contradict himself

00:27:05.760 --> 00:27:06.260
and that's a

00:27:06.260 --> 00:27:07.040
positive quality

00:27:07.040 --> 00:27:07.640
or whatever, and

00:27:07.640 --> 00:27:08.840
it's like, that's

00:27:08.840 --> 00:27:09.660
not exactly right.

00:27:09.800 --> 00:27:10.640
Like, to say that

00:27:10.640 --> 00:27:11.160
you contradict

00:27:11.160 --> 00:27:12.360
yourself is, say,

00:27:12.440 --> 00:27:13.240
like, in one

00:27:13.240 --> 00:27:13.960
passage he says

00:27:13.960 --> 00:27:14.760
the intellect is

00:27:14.760 --> 00:27:15.620
