00:27:23.640 --> 00:27:24.620
they exist, placing

00:27:24.620 --> 00:27:25.500
them side by side

00:27:25.500 --> 00:27:27.100
on a logic, sort

00:27:27.100 --> 00:27:27.460
of a logic puzzle.

00:27:27.460 --> 00:27:27.680
Yeah, that's truth

00:27:27.680 --> 00:27:28.100
claimed.

00:27:29.000 --> 00:27:30.700
Right, in a, like,

00:27:30.820 --> 00:27:31.660
really strictly

00:27:31.660 --> 00:27:33.080
propositional way,

00:27:33.260 --> 00:27:34.500
like, this says the

00:27:34.500 --> 00:27:35.180
opposite of this

00:27:35.180 --> 00:27:35.480
thing.

00:27:35.860 --> 00:27:36.520
And so, what

00:27:36.520 --> 00:27:37.200
you have to do,

00:27:37.300 --> 00:27:37.980
there's a whole

00:27:37.980 --> 00:27:39.920
operation of

00:27:39.920 --> 00:27:41.740
forming something

00:27:41.740 --> 00:27:42.460
that will have

00:27:42.460 --> 00:27:43.580
been seen as a

00:27:43.580 --> 00:27:44.900
contradiction that

00:27:44.900 --> 00:27:46.340
is, that is a

00:27:46.340 --> 00:27:46.840
dramatic

00:27:46.840 --> 00:27:48.180
acontextualizing

00:27:48.180 --> 00:27:49.120
and, you know,

00:27:49.320 --> 00:27:50.280
logisticizing

00:27:50.280 --> 00:27:53.640
logisticizing of a

00:27:53.640 --> 00:27:54.640
series of

00:27:54.640 --> 00:27:55.660
statements or

00:27:55.660 --> 00:27:56.380
utterances or

00:27:56.380 --> 00:27:57.000
whatever else.

00:27:57.700 --> 00:27:59.000
And it's not

00:27:59.000 --> 00:28:00.140
that that's, you

00:28:00.140 --> 00:28:01.000
know, a wrong

00:28:01.000 --> 00:28:01.680
thing to do, that's

00:28:01.680 --> 00:28:02.500
one operation to

00:28:02.500 --> 00:28:03.240
perform, but it's

00:28:03.240 --> 00:28:04.580
also an operation,

00:28:04.800 --> 00:28:04.960
right?

00:28:04.980 --> 00:28:05.780
So it's not like

00:28:05.780 --> 00:28:06.780
Nietzsche doesn't

00:28:06.780 --> 00:28:07.680
contradict himself,

00:28:07.800 --> 00:28:08.540
like, that to me

00:28:08.540 --> 00:28:09.480
would be the strong

00:28:09.480 --> 00:28:10.960
claim that I'd want

00:28:10.960 --> 00:28:11.620
to make, is that

00:28:11.620 --> 00:28:12.460
there are no

00:28:12.460 --> 00:28:13.280
contradictions.

00:28:13.740 --> 00:28:14.380
A contradiction

00:28:14.380 --> 00:28:15.540
also, at least in

00:28:15.540 --> 00:28:16.240
the vulgar sense,

00:28:16.320 --> 00:28:17.640
would presuppose a

00:28:17.640 --> 00:28:18.700
potential resolution,

00:28:19.080 --> 00:28:19.260
right?

00:28:19.320 --> 00:28:20.280
Like this, if a

00:28:20.280 --> 00:28:21.140
paradox is just

00:28:21.140 --> 00:28:22.620
kind of reduced to

00:28:22.620 --> 00:28:23.260
a contradiction,

00:28:23.500 --> 00:28:24.020
which I think is

00:28:24.020 --> 00:28:24.600
kind of what you

00:28:24.600 --> 00:28:24.960
were saying,

00:28:25.040 --> 00:28:26.180
Nathaniel, then

00:28:26.180 --> 00:28:27.160
there's a potential

00:28:27.160 --> 00:28:27.860
for, we could

00:28:27.860 --> 00:28:28.900
resolve this paradox,

00:28:29.020 --> 00:28:29.720
whereas in Nietzsche,

00:28:29.880 --> 00:28:31.160
the ambivalence and

00:28:31.160 --> 00:28:32.000
the fluidity is

00:28:32.000 --> 00:28:33.320
constitutive, and

00:28:33.320 --> 00:28:33.900
that's what lends

00:28:33.900 --> 00:28:34.920
the writing the

00:28:34.920 --> 00:28:36.240
force, I think,

00:28:36.540 --> 00:28:36.680
right?

00:28:36.680 --> 00:28:37.180
Well, I think the

00:28:37.180 --> 00:28:37.920
one way of thinking

00:28:37.920 --> 00:28:38.460
of it is when you

00:28:38.460 --> 00:28:39.260
think of it logically,

00:28:39.500 --> 00:28:40.220
which is, I think,

00:28:40.260 --> 00:28:40.960
the most important

00:28:40.960 --> 00:28:41.720
of thinking about a

00:28:41.720 --> 00:28:42.700
logical contradiction

00:28:42.700 --> 00:28:43.800
is, as John said,

00:28:43.920 --> 00:28:44.760
the principle of

00:28:44.760 --> 00:28:45.460
self-identity,

00:28:45.540 --> 00:28:45.740
right?

00:28:45.840 --> 00:28:46.860
So X, it cannot

00:28:46.860 --> 00:28:48.000
be the case that X,

00:28:48.200 --> 00:28:49.000
both X is

00:28:49.000 --> 00:28:49.840
true and X is

00:28:49.840 --> 00:28:50.480
false at the same

00:28:50.480 --> 00:28:51.040
time, right?

00:28:51.040 --> 00:28:51.820
Where X is the

00:28:51.820 --> 00:28:52.560
same in every

00:28:52.560 --> 00:28:53.040
instance.

00:28:53.580 --> 00:28:54.780
And so the only

00:28:54.780 --> 00:28:56.120
ways, within that

00:28:56.120 --> 00:28:58.300
logical domain, the

00:28:58.300 --> 00:28:59.880
only ways of

00:28:59.880 --> 00:29:00.700
attending to a

00:29:00.700 --> 00:29:01.720
paradox like that is

00:29:01.720 --> 00:29:03.200
to say it is a

00:29:03.200 --> 00:29:04.240
true paradox or it

00:29:04.240 --> 00:29:04.640
is a true

00:29:04.640 --> 00:29:05.460
contradiction, which

00:29:05.460 --> 00:29:06.240
means it's a dead

00:29:06.240 --> 00:29:07.040
end and you don't

00:29:07.040 --> 00:29:07.900
go down there, you

00:29:07.900 --> 00:29:08.740
figured out where

00:29:08.740 --> 00:29:10.740
to go, or it can

00:29:10.740 --> 00:29:11.520
be resolved, which

00:29:11.520 --> 00:29:11.920
means you just

00:29:11.920 --> 00:29:12.480
haven't thought

00:29:12.480 --> 00:29:13.120
about it hard and

00:29:13.120 --> 00:29:13.580
hard enough, which

00:29:13.580 --> 00:29:14.180
means it's not

00:29:14.180 --> 00:29:14.980
actually a

00:29:14.980 --> 00:29:16.640
contradiction, right?

00:29:16.800 --> 00:29:17.720
And so the way

00:29:17.720 --> 00:29:18.480
you could look at

00:29:18.480 --> 00:29:19.120
Nietzsche's

00:29:19.120 --> 00:29:20.860
contradictions, as

00:29:20.860 --> 00:29:21.820
you say, there are

00:29:21.820 --> 00:29:22.760
no contradictions.

00:29:23.020 --> 00:29:23.940
There are only

00:29:23.940 --> 00:29:26.060
intersections of

00:29:26.060 --> 00:29:28.500
varying intensities,

00:29:28.780 --> 00:29:30.040
speeds, relations.

00:29:30.620 --> 00:29:31.420
So, you know, even

00:29:31.420 --> 00:29:32.720
when, you know,

00:29:33.560 --> 00:29:35.460
intellect A and

00:29:35.460 --> 00:29:36.160
intellect B

00:29:36.160 --> 00:29:37.520
intersect with each

00:29:37.520 --> 00:29:38.220
other, you know,

00:29:38.260 --> 00:29:39.560
it's never head

00:29:39.560 --> 00:29:41.580
on, nullifying,

00:29:42.100 --> 00:29:43.140
It's always sort

00:29:43.140 --> 00:29:44.840
of like a, they

00:29:44.840 --> 00:29:45.400
come at each

00:29:45.400 --> 00:29:45.900
other at an

00:29:45.900 --> 00:29:46.980
obtuse angle and

00:29:46.980 --> 00:29:48.320
create singularities,

00:29:48.440 --> 00:29:48.540
right?

00:29:48.540 --> 00:29:49.000
So they don't

00:29:49.000 --> 00:29:50.580
create logical

00:29:50.580 --> 00:29:51.660
relationships between

00:29:51.660 --> 00:29:53.040
propositions, they

00:29:53.040 --> 00:29:54.140
create hesedities.

00:29:54.800 --> 00:29:55.180
That's what a

00:29:55.180 --> 00:29:55.840
paradox is.

00:29:55.940 --> 00:29:56.680
They're generative.

00:29:56.760 --> 00:29:57.620
They're generative

00:29:57.620 --> 00:29:58.380
rather than like

00:29:58.380 --> 00:29:59.240
stifling, right?

00:29:59.260 --> 00:30:00.020
It's not a stopping

00:30:00.020 --> 00:30:01.020
point when you see an

00:30:01.020 --> 00:30:01.640
irresolvable

00:30:01.640 --> 00:30:02.500
contradiction in

00:30:02.500 --> 00:30:02.740
Nietzsche.

00:30:02.920 --> 00:30:03.300
It's not like,

00:30:03.460 --> 00:30:04.220
that's when you

00:30:04.220 --> 00:30:04.840
start thinking.

00:30:05.220 --> 00:30:05.880
That's what allows

00:30:05.880 --> 00:30:06.480
for the partial

00:30:06.480 --> 00:30:07.600
meanings, the

00:30:07.600 --> 00:30:09.040
reversals of

00:30:09.040 --> 00:30:10.120
interpretations, all

00:30:10.120 --> 00:30:10.840
that kind of, all

00:30:10.840 --> 00:30:11.760
the good stuff that

00:30:11.760 --> 00:30:12.480
we like to kind of

00:30:12.480 --> 00:30:13.980
ruminate on, that's

00:30:13.980 --> 00:30:14.460
a product.

00:30:14.460 --> 00:30:15.640
That would be the

00:30:15.640 --> 00:30:16.520
Hegelian way of

00:30:16.520 --> 00:30:17.220
approaching it, right?

00:30:17.280 --> 00:30:18.160
Like what you just

00:30:18.160 --> 00:30:19.540
articulated there is

00:30:19.540 --> 00:30:21.360
that like, and that's

00:30:21.360 --> 00:30:22.260
the sense of the

00:30:22.260 --> 00:30:23.580
contradiction as

00:30:23.580 --> 00:30:24.340
generative because it

00:30:24.340 --> 00:30:24.840
allows you to move

00:30:24.840 --> 00:30:25.380
beyond the

00:30:25.380 --> 00:30:26.420
contradiction, resolve

00:30:26.420 --> 00:30:28.480
it in some, in some

00:30:28.480 --> 00:30:29.680
fashion to move on

00:30:29.680 --> 00:30:31.360
to some, what will

00:30:31.360 --> 00:30:32.120
then be subsequent

00:30:32.120 --> 00:30:32.960
contradiction.

00:30:33.720 --> 00:30:34.360
And, but I think

00:30:34.360 --> 00:30:35.080
it's a different kind

00:30:35.080 --> 00:30:35.680
of claim to say

00:30:35.680 --> 00:30:36.660
there are no

00:30:36.660 --> 00:30:37.420
contradictions.

00:30:37.420 --> 00:30:39.460
Yeah, because

00:30:39.460 --> 00:30:39.920
they wouldn't be

00:30:39.920 --> 00:30:41.040
resolved, right?

00:30:41.100 --> 00:30:41.700
I mean, this is the

00:30:41.700 --> 00:30:43.200
sort of problem,

00:30:43.560 --> 00:30:44.360
question sort of

00:30:44.360 --> 00:30:44.640
thing.

00:30:44.900 --> 00:30:45.360
Yeah, there's not

00:30:45.360 --> 00:30:45.980
the answer, there's

00:30:45.980 --> 00:30:46.720
not the solution.

00:30:47.320 --> 00:30:48.920
It is a singularity

00:30:48.920 --> 00:30:50.120
that is irresolvable,

00:30:50.500 --> 00:30:50.760
right?

00:30:50.940 --> 00:30:51.820
And I mean, it is

00:30:51.820 --> 00:30:53.180
generative, just not

00:30:53.180 --> 00:30:53.860
at the level of the

00:30:53.860 --> 00:30:55.040
proposition, right?

00:30:55.060 --> 00:30:55.960
Not at the level of

00:30:55.960 --> 00:30:57.780
sort of like undoing

00:30:57.780 --> 00:30:58.440
the web.

00:30:58.540 --> 00:30:59.160
It becomes, you

00:30:59.160 --> 00:31:00.440
know, you can see

00:31:00.440 --> 00:31:01.700
apparent

00:31:01.700 --> 00:31:02.700
contradictions are

00:31:02.700 --> 00:31:04.400
bodies, right?

00:31:04.820 --> 00:31:05.620
And so far as the

00:31:05.620 --> 00:31:07.160
contradiction becomes

00:31:07.160 --> 00:31:08.580
a binding between

00:31:08.580 --> 00:31:09.540
two things, a

00:31:09.540 --> 00:31:10.600
relation between

00:31:10.600 --> 00:31:11.620
two things, an

00:31:11.620 --> 00:31:12.700
association between

00:31:12.700 --> 00:31:14.140
two things, then

00:31:14.140 --> 00:31:15.260
it's just a body.

00:31:27.580 --> 00:31:28.820
Say more about that, the

00:31:28.820 --> 00:31:30.840
relation between two

00:31:30.840 --> 00:31:31.580
things becoming a

00:31:31.580 --> 00:31:31.860
body.

00:31:33.860 --> 00:31:34.820
I've just been reading

00:31:34.820 --> 00:31:35.800
a lot of A Thousand

00:31:35.800 --> 00:31:37.600
Plateaus and any set

00:31:37.600 --> 00:31:39.180
of relationships makes

00:31:39.180 --> 00:31:41.360
Up a body, makes a

00:31:41.360 --> 00:31:42.080
body, right?

00:31:42.180 --> 00:31:43.240
In terms of like any

00:31:43.240 --> 00:31:44.380
set of relationships is

00:31:44.380 --> 00:31:45.800
capable of affecting and

00:31:45.800 --> 00:31:46.700
being affected.

00:31:47.700 --> 00:31:49.020
And you add or

00:31:49.020 --> 00:31:50.080
subtract one

00:31:50.080 --> 00:31:51.240
relationship, it's a

00:31:51.240 --> 00:31:52.880
different body.

00:31:53.960 --> 00:31:54.520
And, you know, the

00:31:54.520 --> 00:31:55.700
essence, and, you

00:31:55.700 --> 00:31:57.480
know, this is, this

00:31:57.480 --> 00:31:58.440
could take us back to

00:31:58.440 --> 00:31:59.040
Heidegger, but the

00:31:59.040 --> 00:32:00.420
essence of anything is

00:32:00.420 --> 00:32:01.900
not its essential

00:32:01.900 --> 00:32:03.340
core, it is the

00:32:03.340 --> 00:32:04.240
singularity, the

00:32:04.240 --> 00:32:05.500
haseity of its

00:32:05.500 --> 00:32:06.980
set of relationships.

00:32:07.500 --> 00:32:08.480
What at any given

00:32:08.480 --> 00:32:09.900
moment is it capable

00:32:09.900 --> 00:32:11.980
of linking up to,

00:32:12.060 --> 00:32:13.140
associating with?

00:32:13.360 --> 00:32:13.560
Yeah.

00:32:13.880 --> 00:32:16.240
And what's behind my

00:32:16.240 --> 00:32:17.160
question there, and I

00:32:17.160 --> 00:32:18.140
know the Deleuzean

00:32:18.140 --> 00:32:18.780
resonance, and I've

00:32:18.780 --> 00:32:19.540
never really been able

00:32:19.540 --> 00:32:20.680
to kind of really

00:32:20.680 --> 00:32:23.060
think that, is the

00:32:23.060 --> 00:32:24.020
taste question, which

00:32:24.020 --> 00:32:25.220
is that if the taste

00:32:25.220 --> 00:32:26.100
question is not in the

00:32:26.100 --> 00:32:27.200
intellect, but it's in

00:32:27.200 --> 00:32:28.300
the body for Nietzsche,

00:32:28.480 --> 00:32:29.300
what if the intellect

00:32:29.300 --> 00:32:30.840
is in the business of

00:32:30.840 --> 00:32:32.320
forming bodies, right?

00:32:32.380 --> 00:32:34.060
Like of creating

00:32:34.060 --> 00:32:34.720
different kinds of

00:32:34.720 --> 00:32:35.020
relations.

00:32:35.280 --> 00:32:36.060
So it would be

00:32:36.060 --> 00:32:37.580
another, a next level

00:32:37.580 --> 00:32:39.040
way of reading that

00:32:39.040 --> 00:32:40.380
kind of materialism of

00:32:40.380 --> 00:32:40.680
Nietzsche.

00:32:41.320 --> 00:32:42.160
But I don't even, but

00:32:42.160 --> 00:32:43.320
The intellect is not

00:32:43.320 --> 00:32:44.500
part of the body for

00:32:44.500 --> 00:32:45.140
Nietzsche, right?

00:32:45.180 --> 00:32:46.140
It's just a part of the

00:32:46.140 --> 00:32:46.680
body that's been

00:32:46.680 --> 00:32:47.640
recently developed.

00:32:48.140 --> 00:32:48.960
Right, but I'm just

00:32:48.960 --> 00:32:49.740
saying that if it

00:32:49.740 --> 00:32:51.160
forms contradiction,

00:32:52.160 --> 00:32:53.340
and if we're talking

00:32:53.340 --> 00:32:53.860
about it as the

00:32:53.860 --> 00:32:55.720
relation of statements

00:32:55.720 --> 00:32:57.460
as that which forms

00:32:57.460 --> 00:32:58.780
a body, then we're

00:32:58.780 --> 00:32:59.660
talking, then we

00:32:59.660 --> 00:33:00.820
could very seriously

00:33:00.820 --> 00:33:02.120
talk about the taste

00:33:02.120 --> 00:33:03.920
of concepts.

00:33:04.860 --> 00:33:05.000
Yeah.

00:33:05.000 --> 00:33:05.980
And not just taste

00:33:05.980 --> 00:33:06.560
being...

00:33:06.560 --> 00:33:07.180
Oh, I see what you're

00:33:07.180 --> 00:33:07.400
doing.

00:33:07.780 --> 00:33:08.660
Right, not just taste

00:33:08.660 --> 00:33:09.680
being the corporeal

00:33:09.680 --> 00:33:10.800
thing that manifests

00:33:10.800 --> 00:33:12.820
itself in intellectual

00:33:12.820 --> 00:33:14.660
relations, but like

00:33:14.660 --> 00:33:16.240
really, you know.

00:33:16.260 --> 00:33:16.440
Yeah.

00:33:16.740 --> 00:33:16.980
No.

00:33:17.220 --> 00:33:18.140
And in ways that are

00:33:18.140 --> 00:33:19.600
not sort of independent

00:33:19.600 --> 00:33:21.000
of other sort of more

00:33:21.000 --> 00:33:21.480
like, you know,

00:33:21.540 --> 00:33:22.620
gustatory taste or

00:33:22.620 --> 00:33:23.400
something like that.

00:33:23.620 --> 00:33:23.740
That's right.

00:33:23.800 --> 00:33:24.480
But you'd have to say

00:33:24.480 --> 00:33:25.820
then that...

00:33:25.820 --> 00:33:27.560
So then here, the

00:33:27.560 --> 00:33:28.620
intellect, insofar as

00:33:28.620 --> 00:33:29.460
it's ever existed,

00:33:29.960 --> 00:33:31.560
has always been part

00:33:31.560 --> 00:33:32.380
of the body, always

00:33:32.380 --> 00:33:33.500
existing in relationship

00:33:33.500 --> 00:33:34.580
with the rest of the

00:33:34.580 --> 00:33:34.880
body.

00:33:35.180 --> 00:33:35.920
And the only question

00:33:35.920 --> 00:33:37.520
is, is what role does

00:33:37.520 --> 00:33:37.920
it play?

00:33:38.040 --> 00:33:39.000
Not within the...

00:33:39.000 --> 00:33:39.840
It's a hierarchical

00:33:39.840 --> 00:33:41.120
organization, but it's

00:33:41.120 --> 00:33:42.540
relative position.

00:33:42.740 --> 00:33:43.520
What, you know,

00:33:43.600 --> 00:33:44.900
forces is it able to

00:33:44.900 --> 00:33:46.840
exert and what forces

00:33:46.840 --> 00:33:47.760
does it sort of...

00:33:47.760 --> 00:33:48.780
How does it obey the

00:33:48.780 --> 00:33:49.520
forces that are sort

00:33:49.520 --> 00:33:50.100
of given it?

00:33:50.180 --> 00:33:51.200
And sort of, you

00:33:51.200 --> 00:33:52.180
know, it often has

00:33:52.180 --> 00:33:53.340
that sort of subordinate

00:33:53.340 --> 00:33:55.440
orientation to the

00:33:55.440 --> 00:33:56.440
other forces of the

00:33:56.440 --> 00:33:57.720
body, but that's not

00:33:57.720 --> 00:33:58.820
its essence.

00:33:58.960 --> 00:34:00.260
That's not, you know,

00:34:00.280 --> 00:34:00.980
the only thing it's

00:34:00.980 --> 00:34:01.940
capable of doing.

00:34:02.060 --> 00:34:02.520
So if you're going to

00:34:02.520 --> 00:34:03.480
talk about the

00:34:03.480 --> 00:34:05.040
capacity to create

00:34:05.040 --> 00:34:06.440
tastes of concepts,

00:34:06.440 --> 00:34:07.660
then it would have to

00:34:07.660 --> 00:34:08.580
be then the sort of

00:34:08.580 --> 00:34:09.480
like the activity of

00:34:09.480 --> 00:34:10.720
the intellect, sort

00:34:10.720 --> 00:34:13.580
of now like re...

00:34:13.580 --> 00:34:14.860
like appropriating,

00:34:15.040 --> 00:34:17.320
dominating, working on

00:34:17.320 --> 00:34:18.240
the rest of the body,

00:34:18.480 --> 00:34:18.680
right?

00:34:18.760 --> 00:34:19.440
Well, and he also

00:34:19.440 --> 00:34:20.880
talks specifically like

00:34:20.880 --> 00:34:22.740
concepts do have a

00:34:22.740 --> 00:34:23.680
taste or they have a

00:34:23.680 --> 00:34:24.080
preference.

00:34:24.220 --> 00:34:25.320
They're not impartial,

00:34:25.420 --> 00:34:25.580
right?

00:34:25.620 --> 00:34:26.620
I mean, we've learned

00:34:26.620 --> 00:34:27.400
this from Heidegger,

00:34:27.560 --> 00:34:28.260
from Hegel, from

00:34:28.260 --> 00:34:28.520
Nietzsche.

00:34:29.120 --> 00:34:30.080
Concepts erase

00:34:30.080 --> 00:34:31.720
difference, and that's

00:34:31.720 --> 00:34:32.700
kind of like their

00:34:32.700 --> 00:34:35.240
implicit purpose is to...

00:34:35.240 --> 00:34:36.100
And for Nietzsche

00:34:36.100 --> 00:34:36.900
throughout this book

00:34:36.900 --> 00:34:38.260
one, he seems to

00:34:38.260 --> 00:34:39.300
suggest that every

00:34:39.300 --> 00:34:40.480
philosophical enterprise

00:34:40.480 --> 00:34:42.640
is invested in

00:34:42.640 --> 00:34:45.160
implicitly in a kind

00:34:45.160 --> 00:34:46.520
of desire for

00:34:46.520 --> 00:34:47.880
certainty, and that

00:34:47.880 --> 00:34:49.100
like that threads

00:34:49.100 --> 00:34:49.980
itself throughout the

00:34:49.980 --> 00:34:51.480
whole project in these

00:34:51.480 --> 00:34:52.620
kind of like unconscious

00:34:52.620 --> 00:34:52.960
ways.

00:34:53.100 --> 00:34:54.780
So every concept is in

00:34:54.780 --> 00:34:55.880
some way symptomatic

00:34:55.880 --> 00:34:57.860
of that, of that,

00:34:57.920 --> 00:34:59.080
you know, embedded

00:34:59.080 --> 00:35:00.420
desire, I think.

00:35:00.480 --> 00:35:01.340
I don't know if that's

00:35:01.340 --> 00:35:02.540
a universalizing

00:35:02.540 --> 00:35:04.220
claim for Nietzsche,

00:35:04.360 --> 00:35:05.500
but that seems to be

00:35:05.500 --> 00:35:06.960
that like that's how

00:35:06.960 --> 00:35:08.020
concepts orient

00:35:08.020 --> 00:35:09.300
themselves regardless of

00:35:09.300 --> 00:35:10.660
the intention of the

00:35:10.660 --> 00:35:11.180
philosopher.

00:35:11.380 --> 00:35:12.140
You'd have to think of

00:35:12.140 --> 00:35:13.480
a different form of

00:35:13.480 --> 00:35:14.260
concept here.

00:35:14.380 --> 00:35:15.300
Now you've got me

00:35:15.300 --> 00:35:18.200
really thinking of the...

00:35:18.200 --> 00:35:20.340
So the concept in the

00:35:20.340 --> 00:35:21.860
way that Deleuze takes

00:35:21.860 --> 00:35:22.740
it up in Difference

00:35:22.740 --> 00:35:23.680
and Repetition...

00:35:23.680 --> 00:35:24.060
I was thinking,

00:35:24.160 --> 00:35:24.880
What is Philosophy?

00:35:25.280 --> 00:35:26.180
Well, I'm going to get

00:35:26.180 --> 00:35:26.720
there, yeah.

00:35:26.880 --> 00:35:27.740
But like in Difference

00:35:27.740 --> 00:35:29.180
and Repetition and the

00:35:29.180 --> 00:35:29.980
way that Nietzsche takes

00:35:29.980 --> 00:35:31.380
it up in Truth and Lying

00:35:31.380 --> 00:35:32.960
in a non-moral sense,

00:35:33.020 --> 00:35:33.760
whereas the concept

00:35:33.760 --> 00:35:35.040
aligned the lines of

00:35:35.040 --> 00:35:36.060
that logical position

00:35:36.060 --> 00:35:37.120
which is only at the

00:35:37.120 --> 00:35:37.980
Level of proposition,

00:35:38.120 --> 00:35:38.680
that's a level of

00:35:38.680 --> 00:35:40.460
representation, reflection

00:35:40.460 --> 00:35:43.140
and then ultimately

00:35:43.140 --> 00:35:44.400
equality of erasing

00:35:44.400 --> 00:35:45.560
differences to be able

00:35:45.560 --> 00:35:46.640
to say that X is equal

00:35:46.640 --> 00:35:48.280
to Y or that even that

00:35:48.280 --> 00:35:49.260
X is equal to X.

00:35:49.660 --> 00:35:51.100
And this becomes the

00:35:51.100 --> 00:35:52.220
object of critique for

00:35:52.220 --> 00:35:53.620
both Nietzsche and

00:35:53.620 --> 00:35:54.960
Deleuze in a lot of

00:35:54.960 --> 00:35:55.440
different ways.

00:35:55.500 --> 00:35:56.080
But as soon as you start

00:35:56.080 --> 00:35:56.800
thinking about the

